    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Beeswax, usually dark in color, that is treated by exposure to light and air or with chemicals to remove the color. For beeswax not treated for color uniformity, use "unbleached beeswax."</Note_Text>
